Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

[ Upstream commit b2c93e300a11b419b4c67ce08e16fa1436d8118c ]

Based on patch: https://patchwork.kernel.org/patch/10042045/

